data.description: HOT!!! This 3 bed 2 bath home sits on a large lot perfect for an ADU but thats not all, this property has a garage that was converted into a STUDIO! Seller purchased the property with the conversion and has supplemented their income with the studio. Perfect for investors or first time home buyers. Roof and AC was recently replaced so no more worrying about the rainy days or the hot summers. Bring your competitive offers, seller motivated!
